  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_5_8164-8262",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "8164-8262",
      "markText": "倘若缺乏对自己的爱，对邻舍的爱也是不可能存在的；自我憎恨也一样，不可能在缺乏对别人恨意的前提下独善其身。无法调和的矛盾，最终都会造成可怕的孤立与绝望，就跟那些明目张胆的利己主义者所遭遇的情况一样。",
      "totalCount": 432,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=8164&rangeEnd=8262",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=8164&rangeEnd=8262"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_6_419-473",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "419-473",
      "markText": "这一日已逝去，诚如每一日之所往。我将这一日引到身边，用我那简单而原始、畏畏缩缩的生活方式，温柔地扼杀掉了它。",
      "totalCount": 340,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=419&rangeEnd=473",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=419&rangeEnd=473"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_6_2407-2450",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2407-2450",
      "markText": "大体上心满意足，大体上无痛无灾，蛰伏于这些可堪忍受的普通日子里，可谓是件极美好的事情。",
      "totalCount": 323,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2407&rangeEnd=2450",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2407&rangeEnd=2450"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_5_19094-19155",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "19094-19155",
      "markText": "个体的生活唯有处在两个不同时代、两类不同文化、两种不同宗教彼此交错的地方，才会发展为真正的痛苦，犹如置身地狱一般痛苦难挨。",
      "totalCount": 289,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=19094&rangeEnd=19155",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=19094&rangeEnd=19155"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_6_79861-79951",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "79861-79951",
      "markText": "而这一切，就像今天刚刚开始发展壮大起来的无线电广播一样，实际上只会让人们逃离自身、逃离自己所设定的目标，用越来越频繁的消遣和百无一用的空忙编织而成的密网层层缠住自己，完全无法脱身。",
      "totalCount": 270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=79861&rangeEnd=79951",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=79861&rangeEnd=79951"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_6_4009-4078",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4009-4078",
      "markText": "我本身过的是孤独、无爱、匆忙、完全不修边幅的日子，但却生活在家庭气息与小市民情结浓重的环境中，两者之间时刻存在着的对比，反而令我颇感安心。",
      "totalCount": 266,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4009&rangeEnd=4078",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4009&rangeEnd=4078"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_6_21698-21758",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "21698-21758",
      "markText": "争权之人因权势而毁灭，贪财之人因财富而毁灭，温顺之人因驯良而毁灭，享乐之人因纵欲而毁灭。以此类推，荒原狼则因独立而毁灭。",
      "totalCount": 210,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=21698&rangeEnd=21758",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=21698&rangeEnd=21758"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_5_19215-19300",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "19215-19300",
      "markText": "人类历史上，时常会出现这样的时期，在这个时期里，整个一代人刚好被裹挟在两个时代之间，裹挟在两种截然不同的生活方式之间，乃至失去了全部常识、全部伦理、全部安全感与率真之心。",
      "totalCount": 204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=19215&rangeEnd=19300",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=19215&rangeEnd=19300"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_3_4372-4448",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4372-4448",
      "markText": "黑塞曾经这样写道，人决不能满足于仰慕和崇拜现实，因为这种现实低俗浅薄、永远令人失望、荒凉枯燥，除非证明我们拥有更高的能力来加以否定，否则就无法改变现实。",
      "totalCount": 196,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4372&rangeEnd=4448",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4372&rangeEnd=4448"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_5_5370-5440",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5370-5440",
      "markText": "只有内心真正丰富的人们才办得到。这类人在任何事情上都没什么争强好胜之心，从来不想崭露头角，从不试图说服别人改变什么，从不打算证明自己是对的。",
      "totalCount": 165,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5370&rangeEnd=5440",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5370&rangeEnd=5440"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_6_13374-13399",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "13374-13399",
      "markText": "枯萎的岁月横亘在此方与彼方之间，断绝了彼此的关联。",
      "totalCount": 165,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13374&rangeEnd=13399",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13374&rangeEnd=13399"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_6_88105-88178",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "88105-88178",
      "markText": "凡是知道如何像这样活在当下的人，知道如此无拘无束地生活的人，知道如何开心地欣赏沿途的每一朵小野花、每一个微不足道嬉闹时刻的人，都不会被生活所伤害。",
      "totalCount": 160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=88105&rangeEnd=88178",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=88105&rangeEnd=88178"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_6_76757-76846",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "76757-76846",
      "markText": "你们这些学者和艺术家的脑子里面，充斥着各种花里胡哨的玩意儿，但你们其实也跟其他人一样，都是些普普通通的人。作为普通人，我们的脑子里面，自然也有我们所有普通人共有的白日梦和小把戏。",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=76757&rangeEnd=76846",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=76757&rangeEnd=76846"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_3_1632-1722",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1632-1722",
      "markText": "他认为这证明了自己长期以来的想法，即整个欧洲文明身患重病，行将衰败。救赎必须来自公认的准则之外，也许是东方之光，也许是隐藏在无政府主义理论中的核心，在更高的统一中解决善与恶的对立。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1632&rangeEnd=1722",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1632&rangeEnd=1722"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_6_3683-3743",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3683-3743",
      "markText": "我不知道这究竟是怎么回事：我明明是一头无家可归的荒原狼，是小市民世界的孤僻憎恶者，但却总是寄居在非常小市民阶层的房子里。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3683&rangeEnd=3743",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3683&rangeEnd=3743"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_6_4936-4999",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4936-4999",
      "markText": "过的是体面与健康的生活：早上坚持早起，自觉履行社会职责，大大小小的家庭庆祝活动过得都很适度，周日去教堂做礼拜，晚上也坚持早睡。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4936&rangeEnd=4999",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4936&rangeEnd=4999"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_6_24698-24761",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "24698-24761",
      "markText": "事实上，小市民群体所拥有的生命力，从来就不曾建立在他们当中正常成员们的行为逻辑之上，反而是建立在其中异常成员们的行为逻辑之上。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=24698&rangeEnd=24761",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=24698&rangeEnd=24761"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_6_37088-37164",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "37088-37164",
      "markText": "一个能够理解佛陀的人，一个对人性的天堂与深渊皆有所了解的人，本不应该生活在一个常识、民主、中产阶级教育盛行的世界里——他只是出于胆怯，才选择生活在其中。",
      "totalCount": 143,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=37088&rangeEnd=37164",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=37088&rangeEnd=37164"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_5_13260-13287",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "13260-13287",
      "markText": "人应该以痛苦为荣——每份痛苦都是对我们崇高精神的警醒。",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300017543&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=13260&rangeEnd=13287",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c5d32590813ab6d5ag013b09?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=13260&rangeEnd=13287"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300017543_6_6364-6440",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6364-6440",
